'''前列腺素D<sub>2</sub>'''（'''PGD<sub>2</sub>'''）是[[前列腺素|前列腺素]]的一種。<ref name="pmid12148545">{{cite journal | author = Saito S, Tsuda H, Michimata T | title = Prostaglandin D2 and reproduction | journal = American Journal of Reproductive Immunology (New York, N.Y. : 1989) | volume = 47 | issue = 5 | pages = 295–302 |date=May 2002 | pmid = 12148545 | doi = 10.1034/j.1600-0897.2002.01113.x| url = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/resolve/openurl?genre=article&sid=nlm:pubmed&issn=1046-7408&date=2002&volume=47&issue=5&spage=295| accessdate = 2011-04-09| language = en-US}}</ref><ref name="pmid18836589">{{cite journal | author = Pettipher R, Hansel TT | title = Antagonists of the prostaglandin D2 receptor CRTH2 | journal = Drug News & Perspectives | volume = 21 | issue = 6 | pages = 317–22 | year = 2008 | pmid = 18836589 | doi = 10.1358/dnp.2008.21.6.1246831 | url = http://journals.prous.com/journals/servlet/xmlxsl/pk_journals.xml_summaryn_pr?p_JournalId=3&p_RefId=1246831 | accessdate = 2011-04-09 | language = en-US | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125141252/https://journals.prous.com/journals/servlet/xmlxsl/pk_journals.xml_summaryn_pr?p_JournalId=3&p_RefId=1246831 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 哺乳動物體內，大量的前列腺素只存在於腦部和肥大細胞中，其會影響過敏性疾病如[[哮喘|哮喘]]等的發展。

前列腺素D<sub>2</sub>的研究始於1989年，當時發現其為攝取煙酸後血管舒張（煙堿酸潮紅）的原發性介質。<ref>{{cite journal |pmid = 2475889 | volume=38 | issue=2 | title=Release of markedly increased quantities of prostaglandin D2 in vivo in humans following the administration of nicotinic acid |date=August 1989 | journal=Prostaglandins | pages=263–74 |last1 = Morrow |first1 = JD |last2 = Parsons Wg |first2 = 3rd |last3 = Roberts Lj |first3 = 2nd}}</ref> 2012年發現局部的PGD<sub>2</sub>提高會抑制頭髮生長，<ref name=Garza_et_al_2012>{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1126/scitranslmed.3003122| issn = 1946-6234| volume = 4| issue = 126| pages = 126ra34–126ra34| last = Garza| first = Luis A.,| title = Prostaglandin D<sub>2</sub> Inhibits Hair Growth and Is Elevated in Bald Scalp of Men with Androgenetic Alopecia| journal = Science Translational Medicine| accessdate = 2012-03-22| date = 2012-03-21| url = http://stm.sciencemag.org/content/4/126/126ra34| pmid = 22440736| pmc = 3319975| last2 = Liu| first2 = Y.| last3 = Yang| first3 = Z.| last4 = Alagesan| first4 = B.| last5 = Lawson| first5 = J. A.| last6 = Norberg| first6 = S. M.| last7 = Loy| first7 = D. E.| last8 = Zhao| first8 = T.| last9 = Blatt| first9 = H. B.| displayauthors = 1| archive-date = 2020-11-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201118023633/https://stm.sciencemag.org/content/4/126/126ra34| dead-url = no}}</ref> 研究指出這一現象與一個叫做GPR44的受體有關，後者因此成為了治療[[雄激素性脫髮|雄激素性脫髮]]的[[藥物作用靶點|藥物作用靶點]]，因此數種使用PGD<sub>2</sub>的哮喘藥都開始尋求減少其用量的方法。<ref name="garza_nature_article">{{cite web|url=http://www.nature.com/news/clues-to-the-cause-of-male-pattern-baldness-1.10277|publisher=Nature magazine (News and Comments)|title=Clues to the cause of male pattern baldness|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013552/https://www.nature.com/news/clues-to-the-cause-of-male-pattern-baldness-1.10277|dead-url=no}}</ref>

